Class FillLevelFunction<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<FillLevelFunction.RangeElement<T>>
        • org.flexiblepower.efi.util.FillLevelFunction<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of value that is stored at each element
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<FillLevelFunction.RangeElement<T>>, java.util.Collection<FillLevelFunction.RangeElement<T>>, java.util.List<FillLevelFunction.RangeElement<T>>

    public class FillLevelFunction<T>
extends java.util.AbstractList<FillLevelFunction.RangeElement<T>>
    This class approximates a function where the value is dependent on the fill level of the buffer. It implements a List of FillLevelFunction.RangeElements and can be used in that manner.
